Cell.Text: [S] Look, before I have you help track Mercer down I need to know what you learned from Karliah. I mean everything.
[S] S|Aye. I feared that was the case. From that last entry in Gallus's diary, it looks like he was getting close to exposing Mercer to the Guild. | Anything else?
[S] S|What? Nightingales? But, I always assumed they were just a tale... a way to keep the young footpads in line. | Was there anything else she told you?

Node.Caption: TG07BrynjolfIntroBranchTopic00b: Gallus, Karliah and Mercer were Nightingales.

Cell.Text: [S] S|Trying to make Mercer look bad in front of Maven, eh? Clever lass. | Was there anything else?

Node.Caption: TG07BrynjolfIntroBranchTopic00c: Karliah was behind Goldenglow and Honningbrew.

Cell.Text: Then I have an important task for you. | I need you to break into Mercer's home and search for anything that could tell us where he's gone.

Aye. A gift from the Black-Briars after they kicked the previous family out... place called Riftweald Manor. | He never stays there, just pays for the upkeep on it. Hired some lout by the name of Vald to guard the place.

Node.Caption: TG07BrynjolfIntroConBranchTopic01: He has a house in Riften?

Cell.Text: Be careful, lad. This is the last place in Skyrim I'd ever want to send you.
Be careful, lass.This is the last place in Skyrim I'd ever want to send you.
[S] Just find a way in, get the information and leave. And you have permission to kill anyone that stands in your way.
